  <entry>
    <title>Systemd Service Sample: Hexo Server</title>
    <url>/blog//systemd-service-sample-hexo-server/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Assume that Hexo is already installed, check <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv">Hexo doc<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span> for more information.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/systemd/system/hexo-server.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<a id="more"></a>

<figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption><span>hexo-server.service</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Unit]</span><br><span class="line">Description=Hexo Server</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Service]</span><br><span class="line">Type=simple</span><br><span class="line">User=weili</span><br><span class="line">WorkingDirectory=/home/weili/hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line">ExecStart=hexo server -s -p 8080</span><br><span class="line">Restart=always</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Install]</span><br><span class="line">WantedBy=multi-user.target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Enable, reload and start service.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> hexo-server.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo service hexo-server start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Check the status.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo service hexo-server status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>Hexo</tag>
