    <title>Invisible Markdown Comment in Hexo Generated HTML</title>
    <url>/blog//invisible-markdown-comment-in-hexo-generated-html/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="Objective"><a href="#Objective" class="headerlink" title="Objective:"></a>Objective:</h3><p>Preserve comments in markdown source files and the comments are invisible in generated files.</p>
<h3 id="Trial"><a href="#Trial" class="headerlink" title="Trial"></a>Trial</h3><p>According to the <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9zdGFja292ZXJmbG93LmNvbS9hLzIwODg1OTgw">discussion<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span>, I tried the following four formats to markdown source files.</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">//</span>]: <span class="link">&lt;&gt; (comment1)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">//</span>]: <span class="link"># (commment2)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!--- comment3 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- comment4 --&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Clean and generate.</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Part of the html file generated by command <code>hexo generate</code>.</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;post-body&quot;</span> <span class="attr">itemprop</span>=<span class="string">&quot;articleBody&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!--- comment3 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- comment4 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Okay, the reference-type works.</p>
<h3 id="Code-Snippet"><a href="#Code-Snippet" class="headerlink" title="Code Snippet"></a>Code Snippet</h3><p>For laziness, I create a code snippet to help myself.</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="attr">&quot;Insert invisible comment&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="attr">&quot;scope&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;markdown&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="attr">&quot;prefix&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;//md&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="attr">&quot;body&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="string">&quot;[//]: # (&#x27;$1&#x27;)&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="string">&quot;$2&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">		],</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Insert comment invisible in hexo generated files&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


]]></content>
